.DT
add_goal_event
$MUDNAME$ Creator Help
add_goal_event

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
add_goal_event -  This method adds an event for a goal to react to.
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
void add_goal_event(string goal,
string event)
.EI

.SH Parameters
.SI 5
%^BOLD%^goal%^RESET%^ - the goal the event is for
%^BOLD%^event%^RESET%^ - the event name to react to
.EI

.SH Defined in
.SI 5
/std/npc/goals_inherit.c
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5

This method adds an event for a goal to react to.  This should only be
done from inside the goal initialisation code, and other parts of the
goal.  We will only add things for goals which we know about.
.EP

.SH See also
.SP 5 5
change_priority(), remove_goal_event()

.EP

